track_notes: Hiked in 2022 October. Long approach for me. Combined it with the other ridge peak. You may can do all three, I only managed two. Goat Creek Trail was in good shape. Good progress even though it has great elevation gain. American Ridge Trail starts out good. However, soon starts to faint and disappear. Some recent forest fires do not help and I lost the path many times. Took me just over 4 hours to summit. Flat summit area with some trees. It has a small cairn with plastic tube register.
